Package net.antidot.paf

Main PaF filters package with all interface definitions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Configuration
    The configuration object responsible of the configuration of the filter.
    Document
    This class represents a Document.
    Filter_Info
    Represents the metadata of a filter.
    Handle
    This class represents a connection to the PaF scheduler.
    Layer
    This class represents a layer.
    Pipe_Info
    This class represents metadata about the current Pipe.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DocumentQueue
    Represent a queue of documents.
    Filter
    This class represents a Filter and can extended to define a complex filter.
    GeneratorFilter
    This class is pre-defined specialization of Filter which help to define generator filter.
    Pipe
    The starting class for filters.
    ProcessorFilter
    This class is pre-defined specialization of Filter which help to define processor filter.
    RevisionMetadata
    Represent a revision metadata
    VisitorFilter
    This class is pre-defined specialization of Filter which help to define processor filter.
